\chapter Qt Designer Menu Options

\section1 Menu Options and Functions

\QD provides menu options that perform the actions that are needed to
create applications. Most menu options have additional options such as
dialog boxes that provide more specific functionality. In addition,
many menu options also have corresponding toolbar buttons. This
section of the reference manual will define each menu option and it's
use. For each menu option that invokes dialog boxes or corresponding
toolbar buttons, click the link to go to the appropriate section
within the reference manual which will explain the dialogs and buttons
in detail.

